ra la sopa que Elisenda ha preparado con la nueva dosis de veneno, siendo sorprendido por Tamara." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="2532000" grandparentArt="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1672731.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/69d79cef6ad16397528a860a" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/69d79cef6ad16397528a860a" grandparentRatingKey="69d79cef6ad16397528a860a" grandparentThumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1672731.jpg" grandparentTitle="El Desprecio" grandparentType="show" index="26" parentIndex="1" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1672731.jpg" title="S01:E26" userState="0"><Image alt="S01:E26" type="coverArt" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1672731.jpg"/><Image alt="S01:E26" type="coverPoster" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1672731.jpg"/><Image alt="S01:E26" type="snapshot" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1672731.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1778631554" duration="2665000" endsAt="1778634219" id="69f9e32cb8f58b928776898f" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video><Video guid="plex://episode/69f93a5be9774db7f61d8488" key="/library/metadata/69f93a5be9774db7f61d8488" ratingKey="69f93a5be9774db7f61d8488" summary="Adriana llega a casa de los Perroni y allí Cristian la recibe con un apasionado beso, mientras que Carlos Raúl los observa con dolor." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="2944000" grandparentArt="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1672730.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/69b0b83aba3a6d319e0e710b" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/69b0b83aba3a6d319e0e710b" grandparentRatingKey="69b0b83aba3a6d319e0e710b" grandparentThumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1672730.jpg" gran